high_descs: Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the fridge then turn left and walk to the coffee maker and turn right to face it.
Turn right and walk to the fridge and stand and face it.
Cool the mug off in the fridge and get it back out and close the door.
Go back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug back where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee mug under the coffee makers spout.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the wall, hang a left towards the white fridge, turn left, cross the room and turn right to face the blue coffee maker on top of the counter.
Pick up the white mug sitting on the silver platform of the blue coffee maker on the counter top.
Turn right, head to the white fridge and turn left to face it.
Put the white mug inside the fridge on the top shelf in the middle, let it chill for seven seconds, remove the mug and close the door.
Turn left, cross the room and turn right before the white dishwasher to face the blue coffee maker on the counter top.
Put the chilled mug on the silver platform of the coffee maker on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the fridge, take a left, and go to the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup in the coffee maker.
Take the cup to the fridge.
Cool off the coffee cup in the fridge.
Take the chilled cup back to the coffee maker.
Put the chilled cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup in the coffee maker.
